VASSAL.tools

Class FileFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.filechooser.FileFilter
      • VASSAL.tools.FileFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.FilenameFilter
    Deprecated. 
    Moved to FileFilter.

    @Deprecated
public abstract class FileFilter
extends javax.swing.filechooser.FileFilter
implements java.io.FilenameFilter
    The file filter abstract base class for FileChooser. This class joins together the FileFilter class and the java.awt.FilenameFilter interface so that a uniform file chooser may be used with FileChooser, regardless of the actual (i.e., navive or Swing) file chooser displayed.
